azine |author=MacKenzie, Debora |title=Whales win southern sanctuary |magazine=New Scientist |date=4 June 1994|accessdate=12 September 2015|url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg14219280-900-whales-win-southern-sanctuary/|ref={{harvid|MacKenzie|1994}}}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://iwc.int/sanctuaries |title=Whale Sanctuaries |publisher=International Whaling Commission |accessdate=4 September 2015|ref={{harvid|IWCd}}}}\n*{{cite web | url=http://www.ifaw.org/sites/default/files/whale_watching_worldwide.pdf | title=Whale Watching Worldwide | publisher=International Fund for Animal Welfare | date=2009 | accessdate=26 December 2014 | author=O'Connor, Simon | pages=23\u201324|ref={{harvid|IFAW|2009}}}}\n*{{cite web |url=http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/pdfs/education/viewing_wildlife.pdf |author=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration, NOAA |title=Marine Wildlife Viewing Guidelines |date=January 2004 |accessdate=6 August 2010|ref={{harvid|NOAA|2004}}}}\n*{{cite web |author1=O'Connor S. |author2=Campbell R. |author3=Cortez H. |author4=Knowles T. |year=2009 |accessdate=29 August 2015 |title=Whale Watching Worldwide: tourism numbers, expenditures and expanding economic benefits |url=http://www.ifaw.org/sites/default/files/whale_watching_worldwide.pdf |work=International Fund for Animal Welfare|ref={{harvid|O'Connor|2009}}}}\n*{{cite web|last=Viegas |first=Jennifer| title=Thousands Mourn Dead Whale in Vietnam |url=http://news.discovery.com/animals/thousands-mourn-dead-whale-in-vietnam.html |work=Discovery News |date=23 February 2010|accessdate=15 April 2011|ref={{harvid|Viegas|2010}}}}\n*{{cite web |title=Funeral for a Whale held at Apam |url=http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/artikel.php?ID=87737 | work=Ghana News Agency |publisher=GhanaWeb |date=10 August 2005|accessdate=15 April 2011|ref={{harvid|GNA|2005}}}}\n*{{cite web |url=http://www.artistdirect.com/nad/store/artist/album/0,,197507,00.html |author=Hovhannes, Alan|title=And God Created Great Whales